3 1, 2026]: Sec. 0.5. This chapter does not apply to a case that is
4 brought under IC 34-26-6 to protect an employee from unlawful
5 violence or a credible threat of violence solely related to a dispute
6 arising between two (2) employees over their own personal
7 controversy if the dispute does not involve claims governed by a
8 collective bargaining agreement.
